pandoc 
  to: revealjs
  output-file: edumer_template.html
  standalone: true
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  html-math-method:
    method: mathjax
    url: >-
      https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mathjax/2.7.0/MathJax.js?config=TeX-AMS_HTML-full
  slide-level: 2
  
metadata
  link-citations: true
  width: 1050
  height: 700
  margin: 0.1
  center: false
  navigationMode: linear
  controlsLayout: edges
  controlsTutorial: false
  hash: true
  history: true
  hashOneBasedIndex: false
  fragmentInURL: false
  transition: fade
  backgroundTransition: none
  pdfSeparateFragments: false
  lang: es
  auto-stretch: false
  pagetitle: EDUMER Template
  Author: Equipo EDUMER
  bibliography:
    - ../input/bib/merit-redis-school.bib
  csl: ../input/bib/apa6.csl
  knitr:
    opts_chunk:
      collapse: true
      comment: '#>'
      R.options:
        knitr.graphics.auto_pdf: true
  slideNumber: true
  theme: ../libs/edumer.scss
  title-slide-attributes:
    visibility: false
  transitionSpeed: slow
  autoPlayMedia: true
